title: Washington Post Oracle E-Suite Breach Exposes Data of Over 9,000 Staff and Contractors

content.raw: The Washington Post disclosed a significant data breach affecting more than 9,700 employees and contractors following an external system compromise targeting its Oracle E-Suite infrastructure. The breach, which occurred on July 10, 2025, went undetected for nearly 3.5 months before being discovered on October 27, 2025.
